6323">五星级评论</a>，他写道：“湿腿开始了生活，而Teasdale和Chambers在一个节日上骑了一辆摩天轮，在那里，两人决定给音乐另一个机会。</p><p>在其他地方，湿腿将在少数节日中表演，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2025-line-up-announced-headliners-tickets-3843426">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kneecap-wet-leg-underworld-tv-on-the-radio-announced-for-green-man-2025-3841849">绿人（Green Man）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-blink-182-and-deftones-lead-stacked-shaky-knees-2025-line-up-3841297">摇摇欲坠的膝盖节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nine-inch-nails-doechii-lola-young-more-join-stacked-roskilde-2025-3832591">罗斯基尔德（Roskilde）节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wilderness-2025-festival-line-up-announced-with-basement-jaxx-supergrass-wet-leg-aurora-air-and-more-buy-tickets-3832579">荒野节（Wilderness Festival）</a> ，荒野节（Wilderness Festival），在利物浦（Liverpool）举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-radio-1-big-weekend-2025-sam-fender-wet-leg-myles-smith-and-blossoms-lead-line-up-3832459">广播1大周末</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/50-cent-biffy-clyro-and-snow-patrol-head-eye-catching-trnsmt-2025-festival-line-up-tickets-3818465">TRNSMT 2025</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-the-prodigy-london-grammar-nelly-furtado-lead-boardmasters-2025-line-up-3816511">董事会管理员</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-bicep-cmat-wet-leg-english-teacher-lead-stacked-line-up-for-irelands-all-together-now-2025-3814778">现在在一起，现在在一起</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-khruangbin-wet-leg-mj-lenderman-among-first-names-for-oya-2025-line-up-3813941">。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wet-leg-announce-new-album-moisturizer-with-thunderous-single-catch-these-fists-3850978">潮湿的腿宣布新专辑“保湿霜”，带有雷鸣般的单曲“ Catch the The Fists”</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
